@startuml activity_collect_inventory_data
title Activity Diagram - CollectInventoryData

start
:International Ordering Department initiates stock check;
:System filters candidate sites trading at least one item;
:For each candidate site, generate filtered item list;
:Send stock inquiry requests to candidate sites;
:Sites query their local database for quantities;
:Sites reply with in-stock quantities (0 if out of stock);
:System consolidates all site responses;
:System persists data in Inventory Information File;
stop
@enduml
